<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 21:12:42 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>佩纳表示，尽管与台湾有联系，巴拉圭仍通过南方共同市场向中国开放贸易协议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/paraguay-open-china-trade-deals-via-mercosur-despite-taiwan-ties-pena-says-2024-08-21/</link><description>巴拉圭总统圣地亚哥·佩纳周三表示，尽管巴拉圭与台湾有外交关系，但他对通过南美贸易集团南方共同市场与中国达成贸易协议“完全开放”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 21:10:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/paraguay-open-china-trade-deals-via-mercosur-despite-taiwan-ties-pena-says-2024-08-21/</guid></item><item><title>据英国《金融时报》报道，普华永道因恒大审计而在中国面临 6 个月的禁令</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/pwc-braces-6-month-ban-china-over-evergrande-audit-ft-reports-2024-08-21/</link><description>据英国《金融时报》周三报道，普华永道中国已通知其客户，预计中国当局最早将于 9 月实施为期六个月的业务禁令，作为对倒闭的房地产开发商恒大集团审计的惩罚的一部分。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 20:13:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/pwc-braces-6-month-ban-china-over-evergrande-audit-ft-reports-2024-08-21/</guid></item><item><title>中国电动汽车制造商比亚迪在墨西哥推出新款插电式混合动力SUV</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-electric-carmaker-byd-unveils-new-plug-in-hybrid-suv-mexico-2024-08-21/</link><description>中国电动汽车制造商比亚迪当地总监周三宣布，该公司周三在墨西哥推出了新款插电式 Song Pro 混合动力 SUV，并补充说该车的当地起价将接近 600,000 比索，约合 31,000 美元。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 19:09:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-electric-carmaker-byd-unveils-new-plug-in-hybrid-suv-mexico-2024-08-21/</guid></item><item><title>监管机构称中国央行对长期债券发出警告旨在遏制系统性风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-central-bank-warnings-long-dated-bonds-aim-curb-systemic-risks-watchdog-2024-08-21/</link><description>金融市场协会的一位高级官员表示，中国央行对长期主权债券风险敞口过高发出警告，旨在遏制收益率继续下跌时潜在的系统性风险。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 17:54:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-central-bank-warnings-long-dated-bonds-aim-curb-systemic-risks-watchdog-2024-08-21/</guid></item><item><title>摩根士丹利将墨西哥股票下调至“减持”，并下调中国目标</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/morgan-stanley-cuts-mexico-stocks-underweight-trims-china-targets-2024-08-21/</link><description>出于对司法和选举制度计划改革的担忧，投资银行摩根士丹利周三对墨西哥股市发出“减持”警告，并下调了对中国主要市场的预测。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 13:12:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/morgan-stanley-cuts-mexico-stocks-underweight-trims-china-targets-2024-08-21/</guid></item><item><title>智库警告称，世界大国的战略竞争可能压倒太平洋岛屿</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/world-powers-strategic-rivalry-threatens-overwhelm-pacific-islands-think-tank-2024-08-21/</link><description>一份智库报告在年度太平洋岛屿领导人峰会前警告称，在中国与美国盟友之间的战略竞争中，地缘政治冲击可能会扰乱政治和安全格局，并导致太平洋岛屿地区的团结紧张。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 12:37:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/world-powers-strategic-rivalry-threatens-overwhelm-pacific-islands-think-tank-2024-08-21/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯总统普京在莫斯科会见中国总理李强</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/russias-putin-meets-chinese-premier-li-qiang-moscow-2024-08-21/</link><description>克里姆林宫周三表示，俄罗斯总统普京周三在莫斯科会见了中国总理李强。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 12:28:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/russias-putin-meets-chinese-premier-li-qiang-moscow-2024-08-21/</guid></item><item><title>中国滴滴出行第二季度扭亏为盈</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-didi-global-swings-profit-second-quarter-2024-08-21/</link><description>中国最大的网约车公司滴滴出行第二季度净利润为人民币 14 亿元（合 1.9624 亿美元），而去年同期亏损人民币 3 亿元，该公司继续重建因监管打击而受到严重打击的业务。 。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 11:43:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-didi-global-swings-profit-second-quarter-2024-08-21/</guid></item><item><title>由于产量和全球需求转温和，美国石油出口增长放缓</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/us-oil-export-gains-slow-output-global-demand-turn-tepid-2024-08-21/</link><description>经过多年的强劲增长，美国原油出口增幅预计将在 2024 年趋于稳定，在全球石油需求依然低迷的情况下，国内产量预计将出现疫情以来的最低增幅。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 10:09:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/us-oil-export-gains-slow-output-global-demand-turn-tepid-2024-08-21/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：无情的反弹暂停喘口气</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-08-21/</link><description>塞缪尔·因迪克 (Samuel Indyk) 展望美国和全球市场未来一天</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 10:07:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-08-21/</guid></item><item><title>美国检察官称，强制监禁是乔治桑托斯协议的关键</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/mandatory-prison-was-key-george-santos-deal-us-prosecutor-says-2024-08-21/</link><description>指控这位丑闻缠身的前美国国会议员的联邦检察官周二表示，乔治·桑托斯愿意在监狱中度过至少两年，这是他同意承认欺诈和身份盗窃罪的关键部分。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 10:03:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/mandatory-prison-was-key-george-santos-deal-us-prosecutor-says-2024-08-21/</guid></item><item><title>小米第二季度营收超预期，公布汽车销量</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/xiaomi-q2-revenue-jumps-32-auto-business-smartphone-sales-2024-08-21/</link><description>中国小米公司周三公布的第二季度营收高于预期，首次披露其汽车业务部门的贡献为 62 亿元人民币（8.692 亿美元）。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 09:53:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/xiaomi-q2-revenue-jumps-32-auto-business-smartphone-sales-2024-08-21/</guid></item><item><title>中国机构称欧盟电动汽车关税草案缺乏客观性、公平性</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-body-says-eu-draft-ev-tariffs-lacks-objectivity-fairness-2024-08-21/</link><description>中国一家行业机构周三表示，欧盟对中国电动汽车反补贴调查的调查结果草案缺乏客观性和公平性。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 09:36:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-body-says-eu-draft-ev-tariffs-lacks-objectivity-fairness-2024-08-21/</guid></item><item><title>随着中国出货量的增加，印度4月至7月仍是钢铁净进口国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/india-remains-net-steel-importer-april-july-chinese-shipments-rise-2024-08-21/</link><description>路透社看到的临时政府数据显示，从四月份开始的本财年的前四个月，印度仍然是钢铁净进口国，中国是其最大的合金供应国。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 09:25:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/india-remains-net-steel-importer-april-july-chinese-shipments-rise-2024-08-21/</guid></item><item><title>中国对欧盟乳制品进口展开反补贴调查，以抵制电动汽车关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-opens-anti-subsidy-investigation-into-european-dairy-imports-2024-08-21/</link><description>周三，中国对从欧盟进口的乳制品展开反补贴调查，在布鲁塞尔公布修改后的中国制造电动汽车关税计划的第二天，中国与欧盟的紧张关系加剧。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 07:38:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-opens-anti-subsidy-investigation-into-european-dairy-imports-2024-08-21/</guid></item></channel></rss>